    "title": "<b>Anomalous Void Experiments</b>",
    "body": "<line-indent=10%> We’ve known of Sabrelake’s experiments with void objects for some time now… but rumors of that resulting in an “Internal Assassination Group” has lead us to keep our research a bit more…. quiet.\r\n<br><br>\r\nFindings will be kept in this lab and the identities of anyone working on these experiments will be scrubbed daily.\r\n<br><br>\r\n- Unknown\r\n<br>\n‎",
